project.name: osm-api-js
project.description: Tags used by osm-api-js (A JavaScript library for interacting with the OSM API)

tags.description: Added to changesets when uploading, if the changeset was so big that it had to be chunked (split) into multiple changesets.
Added to changesets if a merge conflict occured and it was automatically resolved (without user interaction).
Added to changesets if a merge conflict occured and it was manually resolved by the user.
Added to changesets if multiple merge conflicts occured, and some were automatically resolved and others were manually resolved.
